      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BURGESS BLACKIE (4) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from five tries. Scored by 4.5 lengths last time (29.65) in an A4 over 480m at this track. Looks suited here and rates on top. SLANEYSIDE CHAMP (2) jumped from the inside and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 2 lengths (29.41) behind GLENBAWN LADY at this track. Can feature again. GOLDMINE SAPHIRE (1) jumped cleanly from the low draw last start to lead all the way (29.29) at this track in an A4 over 480m. Has definite claims. FAIRHILL EMER (6) was well fancied last time on the strength of her recent form but could only manage third (29.97) at this track. Ready to find winning form.",
